parameters: $gameVariables.setValue(21, "Change the direction of the green arrows to guide the rat to the button. Don’t let the snake eat it! ");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoCl.How the hell do I get out of here?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoCl.I was looking for you... But I heard a voice.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MlBaEx.You heard the wind blowing through the crypt.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MlAnOp.Now come with me. You shouldn’t be down here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "It looks like you’re having some trouble. Let’s try it without the snake.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeBaOp.This gate is so old it’s seized up.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MlAnOp.1Hero!? What are you doing in the crypt?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrEx.Oh uhh... I was just visiting my father’s grave and the door was open.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrOp.I didn’t know it connected with the church.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrOp.I’m just curious. What is this place? ");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MlBaEx.This crypt was built with the church a long time ago.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MlBaOp.This is the resting place of the Spanish settlers.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MlAnOp.The priest is on leave. I’ve told you that.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoOp.Still? But you said he came back.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MlAnDe.1Hero. Don’t make me angry with your pestering questions.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeBaEx.Tell me Madalyn. Where are you from?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MlBaEx.I come here from Saint Dame Church. ");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MlBaOp.The church was once part of the university...");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MlBaEx.But it was destroyed in the recent hurricane.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeBaOp.I’m sorry to hear that. It must have been hard for you. ");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MlAnOp.I’m here for now. Until I find what I’m looking for.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MlAnDe.Have you come back to help me? Or just annoy me?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeBaEx.I’ll be exploring the caves with Sofia’s team later tonight.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeBaOp.Whatever you’re looking for Madalyn you’ll have your hands full between Sofia’s crew, and the Eclipse Guild.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MlBaDe.A war for this so-called treasure you seek?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeBaOp.Well... It’s more complicated. Sofia isn’t even looking for the treasure.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MlBaOp.This woman... She is searching the caves for a language?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeBaEx.The rich lady who owns the mansion across the way. ");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeAnEx.I’ve helped you enough Madalyn. It’s time you start spilling the beans.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MlBaEx.I seek something to bring to rest my brother’s soul.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MlBaEx.He has passed on. I am merely following his dying wishes.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MlBaOp.Now tell me. What do you know about Sofia’s quest for this language?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoOp.What was your brother looking for? Do you have some connection to the Tikpak?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MlAnOp.I’m unaware of the Tikpak. Is that what Sofia is after? Is that what she called it?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoEx.No! Well... Yeah... She’s after the Tikpak language. ");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoOp.What does it mean Madalyn? What do you know?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MlBaEx.You’ve done enough 1Hero. I don’t need your help.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeAnEx.I’m leaving to explore those caves with Sofia’s team tonight.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeAnOp.I need to know what’s down there Madalyn. ");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoDe^.What is she up to? Is Madalyn worried about competition from Sofia?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoOp^.Are they looking for the same thing?");
